{"tid":182190,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個叫朋友還錢的方法","createTime":"2017-04-01T06:44:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T09:03:55.000Z","uid":7248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0125c230deedf4ab814dae616c57ed0fe7b7d6db","tid":182190,"uid":7248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T06:44:36.000Z","msg":"雖然唔係多 但自己都唔係有錢 窮學生一個<br />\n點解見我好恰就要恰我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1026ec23a5364eda6a050f7837d7e46f49b123de","tid":182190,"uid":7915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T06:49:31.000Z","msg":"要咁追法就唔係朋友啦"},{"pid":"3592bf78e3497f3f80edd38eda6aaf454e5bd5c5","tid":182190,"uid":37348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T06:51:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要咁追法就唔係朋友啦</blockquote><br />\n啱啊"},{"pid":"835c10b04a11fd25e65f63344953cecc0d56eb46","tid":182190,"uid":78018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T06:52:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>要咁追法就唔係朋友啦</blockquote><br />\n啱啊</blockquote><br />\n啱啊"},{"pid":"5893ffbac69acfb0fc5234935f89888c353fbb74","tid":182190,"uid":1401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T06:53:19.000Z","msg":"中學唔係有訓導咩？"},{"pid":"f118c12b7231c68beccd36a196104439f51bf849","tid":182190,"uid":2411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T06:55:10.000Z","msg":"追到佢還嘅話多數都無朋友做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8a8d0231877e663186fec99c7c7757203ec927","tid":182190,"uid":77481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T06:59:23.000Z","msg":"借得錢都預左有一半機會無左呢個朋友<br />\n借完仲要追佢還就算撚數啦 九成唔會做翻朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46779bf63b8640c2b4d9898126a4df78bc48521e","tid":182190,"uid":7248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T07:11:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>借得錢都預左有一半機會無左呢個朋友<br />\n借完仲要追佢還就算撚數啦 九成唔會做翻朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔想係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc0d86ce8ec42cdaca843377381841a526b41def","tid":182190,"uid":9215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T07:49:16.000Z","msg":"算啦樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係朋友你借錢比佢係唔會催佢還<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為你會知道人地一定會還<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我同班fd互相借錢渡難從來唔怕難數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算真係等錢洗追數都唔洗私私縮縮 <br />\n直接叫人傍水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你問個fd收數都驚証明你地交情都不過如此<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"975cb75efc86d2d334f7acfd88c164ba6dcc2296","tid":182190,"uid":7248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T07:56:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>算啦樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係朋友你借錢比佢係唔會催佢還<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為你會知道人地一定會還<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我同班fd互相借錢渡難從來唔怕難數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算真係等錢洗追數都唔洗私私縮縮 <br />\n直接叫人傍水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你問個fd收數都驚証明你地交情都不過如此<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉 我都唔知<br />\n我有提過想佢還錢 但佢好完我之後就冇左會事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56665948dd30e668d84be5f7acb7947148e08143","tid":182190,"uid":9253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T08:02:00.000Z","msg":"樓上講得好岩，真朋友係你唔叫 佢都會主動還<br />\n而你自己等錢用既話 直接同佢講還錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至於樓主你借比果:個 佢應該無當你係朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c9060c95135485b0495400f6cd832962ca2ea5","tid":182190,"uid":78252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T08:02:51.000Z","msg":"問佢借返錢，然後，呀還掂上次借你x蚊，打和囉"},{"pid":"7902cdeeb0d1d7bd4d5d4125a67bbdd19ad67b1c","tid":182190,"uid":7248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T08:04:39.000Z","msg":"我當佢真心朋友 唔想用咩手段迫佢還<br />\n要用錢睇清楚一個人真係好sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cfd65d7878178cd6a9746701d377fa0bbbc2f19","tid":182190,"uid":86423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T08:16:10.000Z","msg":"問佢借番當還<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3081092c3444ce8c0467960c1ddaf1f9a1d219a6","tid":182190,"uid":25204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T08:19:09.000Z","msg":"我會直接屌七佢 但都係唔會還<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"004bbe99c99b9f9276a746485074462aa3b5ebc4","tid":182190,"uid":2819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T08:23:16.000Z","msg":"窮學生仲可以借錢比人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30e85fe28c0d4a56cf08fd5799a9abb22885956","tid":182190,"uid":7248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T08:26:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>窮學生仲可以借錢比人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實唔係借現金 係旅行幫佢買嘢"},{"pid":"f1c35e0ad016660401fb4f131f9d993eafdfa1e5","tid":182190,"uid":22624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T08:27:59.000Z","msg":"問佢借錢"},{"pid":"a64752cb05fe10bb92620c4c6abc968464993009","tid":182190,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T08:48:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e752620a83e0427805f3934da6e9e4de2afa808d","tid":182190,"uid"